#ROOM
Vnum     12900
Name     &dThe Deadmines - Instance Portal&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     You have stepped through the swirling instance portal deep beneath the
Moonbrook barn. The air here is damp and smells of undisturbed earth
and black powder. The tunnel slopes sharply downward into the dark.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    12901
Desc      The tunnel descends deeper into the mines.
~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12901
Name     &dThe Dusty Tunnels&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The walls of this narrow tunnel are supported by rotting wooden beams.
The sound of pickaxes striking stone echoes faintly from the east. The
Defias Brotherhood has been busy excavating these old shafts.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12902
Desc      The tunnel continues east.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    12900
Desc      The path back to the instance portal.
~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12902
Name     &dCart Track Crossing&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     Rusted iron cart tracks crisscross the stone floor here. Several wooden
mine carts sit abandoned, filled with useless rubble. The tracks lead
northward into a wider excavation area.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12903
Desc      The tracks lead north.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12901
Desc      The dusty tunnel leading back.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 12901 4 12902
  Reset E 0 12903 1 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12903
Name     &dThe Excavation Site&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The tunnel widens into a larger staging area. Torches sputter on the
walls, casting long, dancing shadows. Evokers and miners coordinate
their efforts here, moving massive amounts of stone to clear a path
deeper into the mountain.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12904
Desc      A heavy wooden barricade blocks the way east.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12902
Desc      The cart track crossing.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 12900 6 12903
  Reset E 0 12900 1 6
  Reset E 0 12901 1 16
Reset M 0 12903 4 12903
  Reset E 0 12900 1 6
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12904
Name     &dThe Ogre's Guard Post&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The tunnel ends in a massive chamber sealed by enormous, iron-banded
wooden doors. The ground is littered with chewed bones and broken
mining equipment. This is the domain of the Brotherhood's brute enforcer.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12905
Desc      The heavy wooden doors lead to the Mast Room.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12903
Desc      The excavation site.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 12902 2 12904
  Reset E 0 12902 1 16
Reset M 0 12904 6 12904
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12905
Name     &dThe Heavy Wooden Doors&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     You have passed Rhahk'Zor's guard post. The immense wooden doors have
been forced open, revealing a breathtakingly large subterranean cavern.
A complex network of wooden walkways hangs suspended in the dark.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12906
Desc      You step out onto the upper walkway.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12904
Desc      The ogre's guard post.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 12904 6 12905
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12906
Name     &OThe Mast Room - Upper Walkway&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     You stand on a rickety wooden platform suspended high above the cavern
floor. Huge gaps in the planks reveal a dizzying drop. Below, you can
see dozens of goblins and Defias members working on massive wooden masts.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12907
Desc      The walkway continues south.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12905
Desc      The heavy doors.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 12900 6 12906
Reset M 0 12904 6 12906
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12907
Name     &OThe Mast Room - Winding Ramp&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The wooden walkway spirals downwards along the cavern wall. The sound
of buzzing saws and shouting goblins grows significantly louder. The
sheer scale of the Defias operation is beginning to become clear.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12906
Desc      The upper walkway.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    12908
Desc      The ramp descends to the cavern floor.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 12901 4 12907
  Reset E 0 12903 1 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12908
Name     &OThe Mast Room - Cavern Floor&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     You have reached the bottom of the cavern. Massive tree trunks, stripped
of their bark, lie everywhere. Defias workers and goblin engineers are
frantically shaping the wood for some massive, unseen project.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12909
Desc      A pathway leads toward the Lumber Mill.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    12907
Desc      The ramp leading back up.
~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12909
Name     &OThe Lumber Mill Bridge&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     A sturdy stone bridge spans a deep chasm within the cavern. On the
other side, you can see a massive, multi-level wooden structure built
into the rock. Black smoke billows from its chimneys.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12910
Desc      The entrance to the Lumber Mill.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12908
Desc      The Mast Room floor.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 12900 6 12909
  Reset E 0 12901 1 16
Reset M 0 12903 4 12909
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12910
Name     &OThe Lumber Mill - Main Floor&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The noise here is deafening. Enormous waterwheels power massive
grinding gears and saws. Goblins rush about with planks of wood. In the
center of the room, a massive mechanical shredder is currently powered
down, but its pilot looks eager for a fight.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12909
Desc      The bridge back to the Mast Room.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    12911
Desc      A ramp leads up to the Shredder platform.
~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12911
Name     &OSneed's Shredder Platform&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     This elevated platform overlooks the entire Lumber Mill. It is covered
in grease, sawdust, and scattered tools. Sneed controls the lumber
production from here, strapped tightly into his lethal, blade-covered
machine.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12912
Desc      A door leads toward the Goblin Foundry.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    12910
Desc      The ramp leads down to the main floor.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 12905 2 12911
  Reset E 0 12904 1 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12912
Name     &OTunnel to the Foundry&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     Leaving the deafening saws of the Lumber Mill behind, this tunnel grows
increasingly hotter the further east you walk. The walls glow with the
faint orange light of molten metal.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12911
Desc      Sneed's platform.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 12907 4 12912
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12913
Name     &RThe Goblin Foundry - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     You step out of the tunnel and into a blistering wave of heat. The
Foundry is massive, lit entirely by the hellish orange glow of open
smelting pits. The air is thick with ash and the metallic tang of
melting iron.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12914
Desc      The main floor of the Foundry.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12912
Desc      The tunnel leading back to the Lumber Mill.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 12909 4 12913
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12914
Name     &RThe Goblin Foundry - Main Floor&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     Rivers of molten metal run through heavy stone trenches on either side
of you. Goblin craftsmen are working furiously, pouring the metal into
molds to create weapons, armor, and massive iron plates for an unknown
project.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12915
Desc      Gilnid's personal forge.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12916
Desc      The rear exit of the Foundry.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12913
Desc      The entrance of the Foundry.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 12907 4 12914
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12915
Name     &RGilnid's Forge&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     This raised stone platform overlooks the rest of the Foundry. The largest
and hottest furnace in the cavern roars here. Gilnid, the goblin
overseer, stands here directing the flow of molten iron and screaming
at his subordinates.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12914
Desc      The main floor of the Foundry.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 12906 2 12915
  Reset E 0 12906 1 16
  Reset E 0 12908 1 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12916
Name     &RThe Foundry Rear Exit&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The heat begins to dissipate slightly as you reach the eastern edge of
the Foundry. The stone trenches of molten iron stop here, giving way
to a dark, natural cavern path that slopes steeply downward.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12917
Desc      The cavern descends into the darkness.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12914
Desc      The main floor of the Foundry.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 12918 2 12916
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12917
Name     &dCavern Descent&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The path winds sharply downward. The walls here are slick with moisture,
and the orange glow of the Foundry is entirely swallowed by the shadows.
You can hear the faint, echoing sound of water lapping against stone far
below.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12918
Desc      The path continues to descend.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12916
Desc      The rear exit of the Foundry.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 12909 4 12917
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12918
Name     &dDefias Checkpoint&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The tunnel widens into a small cavern. A makeshift barricade of wooden
crates and barrels has been set up here to protect the approach to the
docks. Defias Pirates stand guard, eyeing the shadows suspiciously.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12919
Desc      A small side cave holding explosive supplies.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12920
Desc      The tunnel opens up toward a massive door.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12917
Desc      The cavern descent.
~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12919
Name     &dThe Powder Room&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     This small, dry offshoot of the main cavern is heavily guarded. Stacks
of wooden barrels marked with skull and crossbones line the walls. The
smell of sulfur and black powder is overwhelmingly strong here. One wrong
spark could collapse the entire mountain.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12918
Desc      The Defias checkpoint.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 12914 4 12919
Reset M 0 12908 4 12919
Reset O 0 12907 1 12919
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12920
Name     &dApproach to the Docks&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The narrow tunnel opens up into an impossibly large subterranean cavern.
The salty smell of the ocean is unmistakable now. Ahead of you, the
path is completely blocked by a structure of colossal proportions.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12921
Desc      A massive iron cannon points at a closed door.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12918
Desc      The Defias checkpoint.
~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12921
Name     &OThe Defias Cannon&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     A massive, black iron cannon sits in the center of the path, aimed
point-blank at a colossal ironclad door to the east. Several heavy
cannonballs and empty powder kegs are scattered around its base. It
looks like it was dragged down here for a very specific purpose.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12922
Desc      The towering Ironclad Door.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12920
Desc      The approach tunnel.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset O 0 12909 3 12921
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12922
Name     &dThe Ironclad Door&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     You stand before the shattered, burning remains of a pair of doors so
massive they defy logic. The smell of the blasted black powder hangs
heavy in the air. Through the smoking breach, you can hear the lapping
of water and the shouts of pirates.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12923
Desc      You step through the blasted doorway into the Cove.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12921
Desc      The Defias Cannon.
~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12923
Name     &cIronclad Cove - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     You step through the ruined doors and your breath catches. You are standing
in an impossibly massive underground cove. A subterranean saltwater lake
stretches out before you. Moored at the far docks is an enormous, fully
constructed warship: The Defias Juggernaut.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12924
Desc      The path winds down to the water's edge.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12922
Desc      The shattered Ironclad Doors.
~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12924
Name     &cIronclad Cove - Water's Edge&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The rocky path meets the calm, dark water of the underground lake. To
the south, a sturdy wooden dock extends out toward the towering warship.
Defias pirates patrol the area, highly alerted by the explosion.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12925
Desc      The beginning of the wooden docks.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12923
Desc      The entrance of the cove.
~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12925
Name     &OThe Wooden Docks - Start&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You step onto the creaking wooden planks of the docks. Heavy ropes and
mooring cleats line the edges. The sheer size of the Juggernaut looming
ahead is intimidating.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12924
Desc      The water's edge.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12926
Desc      The docks continue toward the ship.
~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12926
Name     &OThe Wooden Docks - Center&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     This wide section of the docks serves as a staging area for loading cargo
onto the ship. Dozens of crates are stacked here. A massive tauren stands
in the center of the docks, blocking the path forward.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12925
Desc      The start of the docks.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12927
Desc      The end of the docks, near the gangplank.
~
#ENDEXIT

