#ROOM
Vnum     12927
Name     &OThe Wooden Docks - End&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You stand at the very end of the wooden docks. The massive black hull of
the Defias Juggernaut rises straight up like a wooden wall. A heavy,
reinforced gangplank stretches upwards, connecting the docks to the
main deck of the ship.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12926
Desc      The center of the docks.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12941
Desc      A small, hidden path runs along the shoreline.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    12928
Desc      Climb the gangplank to the ship.
~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12928
Name     &OThe Defias Juggernaut - Gangplank&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You are walking up the steep, swaying gangplank. Below you is the dark,
freezing water of the cove. Above you, heavily armed pirates wait to
repel boarders.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    12929
Desc      The main deck of the ship.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    12927
Desc      The docks below.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 12916 6 12928
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12929
Name     &OThe Defias Juggernaut - Main Deck (Aft)&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You step onto the pristine wooden deck of the warship. The engineering
is flawless, a testament to VanCleef's skill as a stonemason and builder.
To the north, the deck stretches forward. Behind you are the stairs up
to the captain's wheel.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12930
Desc      The midship deck.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    12933
Desc      The captain's wheel.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    12928
Desc      The gangplank.
~
#ENDEXIT

Reset M 0 12916 6 12929
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12930
Name     &OThe Defias Juggernaut - Main Deck (Midship)&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The center of the ship is dominated by the massive central mast. Ropes
and rigging stretch up into the darkness of the cavern ceiling. Defias
Squallshapers channel magic here, preparing to summon the winds needed
to sail the ship out of the mountain.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12931
Desc      The forward deck.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12929
Desc      The aft deck.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    12936
Desc      A hatch leads down to the lower decks.
~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12931
Name     &OThe Defias Juggernaut - Main Deck (Forward)&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The deck begins to narrow here as it approaches the bow. Several heavy
ballistae are mounted to the rails, pointed toward the cave entrance.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12932
Desc      The bow of the ship.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12930
Desc      The midship deck.
~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12932
Name     &OThe Defias Juggernaut - Bow&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You stand at the very front of the ship. A beautifully carved wooden
figurehead looks out over the dark waters. From here, you have a perfect
view of the colossal cavern that hides the Defias fleet.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12931
Desc      The forward deck.
~
#ENDEXIT

