Reset M 0 12915 2 12932
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12933
Name     &OThe Defias Juggernaut - Captain's Wheel&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     This raised platform at the rear of the ship holds the massive wooden
steering wheel. Captain Greenskin stands here, looking down at the deck
with a scowl. A set of elegant wooden doors to the east leads into the
captain's cabin.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12934
Desc      The entrance to the captain's cabin.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    12929
Desc      The aft main deck.
~
