#ROOM
Vnum     12934
Name     &OThe Defias Juggernaut - Cabin Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     You step into a richly furnished antechamber. Fine rugs and looted
paintings from Westfall adorn the walls. Defias Companions lounge here,
guarding the final set of doors that lead to the mastermind himself.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    12935
Desc      VanCleef's personal quarters.
~
#ENDEXIT

#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12933
Desc      The captain's wheel outside.
~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12935
Name     &OVanCleef's Cabin&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The heart of the Defias Brotherhood. Architectural blueprints for Stormwind
City are pinned to the walls alongside tactical maps outlining its
destruction. Edwin VanCleef stands here in the shadows, his cruel
blades drawn and ready.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12934
Desc      The cabin entrance.
~
