#ROOM
Vnum     12937
Name     &OThe Defias Juggernaut - Cannon Deck (Port)&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     Row upon row of heavy black iron cannons face out of the open gunports.
Stacks of cannonballs and powder kegs sit ready. It is clear that this
ship was built to besiege a city.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    12936
Desc      The center of the lower deck.
~
#ENDEXIT

#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12938
Name     &OThe Defias Juggernaut - Cannon Deck (Starboard)&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     More heavy cannons line the starboard side. The sheer weight of the iron
here makes the entire deck groan slightly as the ship rocks in the
underground waters.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    12936
Desc      The center of the lower deck.
~
#ENDEXIT

