#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     12939
Name     &OThe Defias Juggernaut - Cargo Hold&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     You descend into the dark, damp belly of the ship. The cargo hold is
packed to the ceiling with stolen grain, weapons, and gold from the
plundered farms of Westfall.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    12936
Desc      The lower deck.
~
