Vnum     12940
Name     &OThe Defias Juggernaut - Bilge&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     You are at the very bottom of the ship, below the waterline. Seawater
sloshes ankle-deep around your boots. It smells foul and stagnant down
here.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    12939
Desc      The cargo hold.
~
