Vnum     12941
Name     &cIronclad Cove - Hidden Shore&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     Following a small, muddy path around the edge of the water from the docks,
you discover a secluded, sandy shore. A bubbling cauldron sits over a fire.
This is where Cookie, the ship's murloc chef, prepares the crew's meals.
~
