Vnum     12942
Name     &dIronclad Cove - Secret Exit&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     A small, natural tunnel opens up in the rock face just past the shore.
You can smell fresh air and feel a breeze coming from the east. This
must be the secret exit that leads out to the western shores of Westfall.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    12941
